high_descs: Turn right and turn left to the coffeetable.

Turn left, move forward, turn right, move forward and turn right again. Turn left, move forward and turn right to the fridge.

Place the eggplant in the sink.

Pick up the eggplant on the coffee table.

Put the eggplant in the upper drawer of the fridge and take it out after some time.
